02:08.709 --> 02:10.917
Texas is
a bizarro world.

02:11.000 --> 02:13.583
Jock Jeffcoat's a pariah
at Zabar's

02:13.667 --> 02:16.041
but he's the second coming
on the 29th parallel.

02:16.125 --> 02:19.875
