hypoallergenic?--

05:09.291 --> 05:13.625
stuff that makes my eyes
glaze over.

05:13.709 --> 05:14.709
Sorry to hear that.

05:14.792 --> 05:15.834
It'll all be fine.

05:15.917 --> 05:17.375
As soon as we get
the first location open

05:17.458 --> 05:18.291
