of Fuck Ups Fucking Up.

07:51.750 --> 07:55.875
Today, at Axe Cap,
it's comp day.

07:55.959 --> 07:59.875
And so, as always, I'm reminded
of the best day of my life.

07:59.959 --> 08:01.333
The day that this man,

08:01.417 --> 08:03.625
Bill McGann
of McGann Commodities,

08:03.709 --> 08:05.875
told me I didn't have
enough Blarney in me.

08:05.959 --> 08:08.375
